<i># Love is blindness</i>

54:37.880 --> 54:40.850
<i># I'm so sick of it
I don't wanna see</i>

54:40.920 --> 54:43.287
<i># Why don't you just take the night</i>

54:43.520 --> 54:45.727
<i># And wrap it all around me, now</i>

54:46.040 --> 54:49.965
<i># Oh, my love</i>

54:50.040 --> 54:52.646
<i># Blindness</i>

54:52.880 --> 54:56.202
<i># Oh, love is blindness</i>

54:56.360 --> 54:59.045
<i># Mmm-mmm...</i>

